    "extract": "Enlight Renewable Energy is a publicly traded company, headquartered in Israel, that builds and operates solar and wind power facilities. Its shares are traded on the Tel Aviv Stock Exchange (TASE: ENLT) and on Nasdaq (ENLT) following the company's United States initial public offering in February 2023. In addition to solar and wind, Enlight develops utility-scale energy storage and agrivoltaic (\"agro solar\") projects integrating agricultural land use with photovoltaic generation."
